@startuml

title Mongo Engine Execution Flow

actor User

participant "mongo_engine.py" as Engine
participant "JSON Configuration" as JSON
database MongoDB

User -> Engine : Execute\npython mongo_engine.py config.json

Engine -> JSON : Read configuration
JSON --> Engine : action + parameters

Engine -> MongoDB : Execute operation\n(find / insert / update / delete / aggregate)

MongoDB --> Engine : Results

Engine -> User : Print formatted output

@enduml